---
title: Oven-Baked Beef Meatballs with Roast Veggie Couscous & Herbs
description: The trick to super tender meatballs? Baking them of course! It allows for plenty of moisture and flavour to stay in your meatballs
where they belong. Veggie-loaded couscous and aromatic herbs add an indulgent touch to this nourishing dish.

